&lt;a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=191159&gt;My Magelo Profile &lt;/a&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jochangaladar>Jochan Galadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 816<br> <font color=#333333>(12/30/02 6:36:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=492.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Magician's Host Vs Shaman's Spirit</span><hr size=1> Those who have Host have observed that the dps on their minipets exceeds the dps of the Shaman minipets.  Also, even though our skill only has a duration of 30 seconds, our total damage done also exceeds the Shaman's skill. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pimm>Pimm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#333333>(12/30/02 8:42:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=492.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Magician's Host Vs Shaman's Spirit</span><hr size=1> That might be so but it kinda sucks that their wolves can stand up to mobs quad hitting for 500's and our little elementals would go SPLAT to that kinda punishment faster then a Chanter that's slow gets resisted right after tashing a mob =D.<br>
